caption.p: Charge–discharge profiles of ( a) SVO-0 and ( b) SVO-100 in different cycles; ( c) cycling stability and Coulombic efficiency (CE) of SVO-0, SVO-10, SVO-50, SVO-100 at a current density of 50 mA g −1; and ( d) rate capability of SVO-0, SVO-10, SVO-50, SVO-100 at current densities from 50 mA g −1 to 800 mA g −1.
